26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_bios_image.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include <subdev/bios.h>
30#include <subdev/bios/image.h>
31#include <subdev/bios/pcir.h>
32#include <subdev/bios/npde.h>
33
34static bool
35nvbios_imagen(struct nvkm_bios *bios, struct nvbios_image *image)
36{
37 struct nvkm_subdev *subdev = &bios->subdev;
38 struct nvbios_pcirT pcir;
39 struct nvbios_npdeT npde;
40 u8 ver;
41 u16 hdr;
42 u32 data;
43
44 switch ((data = nvbios_rd16(bios, image->base + 0x00))) {
45 case 0xaa55:
46 case 0xbb77:
47 case 0x4e56: /* NV */
48 break;
49 default:
50 nvkm_debug(subdev, "%08x: ROM signature (%04x) unknown\n",
51 image->base, data);
52 return false;
53 }
54
55 if (!(data = nvbios_pcirTp(bios, image->base, &ver, &hdr, &pcir)))
56 return false;
57 image->size = pcir.image_size;
58 image->type = pcir.image_type;
59 image->last = pcir.last;
60
61 if (image->type != 0x70) {
62 if (!(data = nvbios_npdeTp(bios, image->base, &npde)))
63 return true;
64 image->size = npde.image_size;
65 image->last = npde.last;
66 } else {
67 image->last = true;
68 }
69
70 return true;
71}
72
73bool
74nvbios_image(struct nvkm_bios *bios, int idx, struct nvbios_image *image)
75{
76 memset(image, 0x00, sizeof(*image));
77 do {
78 image->base += image->size;
79 if (image->last || !nvbios_imagen(bios, image))
80 return false;
81 } while(idx--);
82 return true;
83}
